    "description": "<p>   <span style=\"font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">Amazing Art Shuttle is a vibrant and energetic art education company, seeking to inject fun and excitement into Singapore&rsquo;s Art Education scene. Led by a house full of young minds, we offer fresh, original concepts and ideas, striving to bring about engaging and interactive art events, workshops and programmes for all. Aside from organizing and designing art events and activities for the mass public, Amazing Art Shuttle provides weekly quality art classes to children (4 to 12 years old) living in the heartlands to bring about a better understanding of the benefits of art through an immersive and integrated learning curriculum.&nbsp;</span></span></p>  ",
